condclass matter at post office at Atlanta under act of March 3 1373 HEARSTS SUNDAY AMERICAN and THE ATLANTA GEORGIAN wHI be mailed to \u00fcb fibers anyuher in the United StwG Canada and Mexico one month for three months for fl 5 six months Er 350 and one year for 00 change of address made as often as dr l Foreign subscription r ates on application A Government Central Bank Is a Good Dem ocratic Ideal Mr Jacob H Schiff has conferred a distinct service by his speech in regard to currency legislation One does not have to agree with him in every point to appreciate the value and the illuminating character of his utterances Mr Schiffs speech can hardly be considered alarmist The points that he makes are First That the currency legislation before Congress ought to be completed as speedily as may be since delay mean usneer tainty and uncertainty is always a disturbing influence in the business world Second That despite the desirability of a prompt conclusion of the currency question nevertheless"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-05-22T12:58:30.451Z", "group": ["ndnp/gu", "digital-library-of-georgia-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89053729/1913-11-11/ed-6/?sp=18", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_kesil_ver01:data:sn89053729:00393344581:1913111106:0849/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=261&w=214", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_kesil_ver01:data:sn89053729:00393344581:1913111106:0849/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=523&w=429", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_kesil_ver01:data:sn89053729:00393344581:1913111106:0849/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1047&w=859", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/gu/batch_gu_kesil_ver01/data/sn89053729/00393344581/1913111106/0849.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 18, "language": ["english"], "location": ["georgia", "united states", "atlan